        Product description

        I stopped saving the world!
        The origin of the "Atelier" series is a full remake for a 25th anniversary.

        For Academy graduation, Alchemy adventures and all things you can do
        Enjoy the slow life PRG in your studio.

        Story
        The protagonist Marie is a student of the Royal School of Witches (also known as Academy).
        One day teacher can give her alchemy studio for graduation examinations.

        The graduation exam is completed by the teacher to convince the item.

        So you can raise your alchemy skills or collect ingredients in the mixture
        Collect references, tools, and money for hiring adventurers...
        There are plenty of things you can do for formula, combat, and requests.

        Your freedom to get started!
        Get your own way to enjoy your academy graduation.

        Redesigned graphics!
        The character stands and event stills have been renewed, and the 2D animation is implemented in the standing picture.
        It also implements 3D models of characters and stages. When you are traveling or exploring, the cute mini characters will move.

        Add many new elements!
        The "indefinite mode" allows you to play slowly without burning it.
        The charm of the characters is deeply "interaction event".
        The attack of the path is "Project of Inglido"
        In addition, there are many features such as changing difficulty levels, and redecorating the studio.

        From the Manufacturer

        I stopped saving the world.

        The "Atelier" series is the origin of Marie and adds a number of new elements to complete remake!

        "Slow Life RPG" where students Mary struggles to alchemy, adventure, and fulfillment

        Updated graphics! Modern technology makes marries more lively and vivid!

        The character stands and event stills have been renewed, and the 2D animation is implemented in the standing picture.

        It also implements 3D models of characters and stages.

        When you are traveling or exploring, the cute mini characters will move.

        The origin of the Atelier series that is easier to play with the latest model.

        The original version has a simple and highly freedom of play without the same possibilities.

        We have expanded tutorial and guide to various specifications.

        Furthermore, the specifications of the city have been revised to match the latest model for transportation and retrieval of the city.

        It is comfortable and easy to play.

        Lifetime Mode

        You can play slow and slow rising!

        "Graduation in 5 years" mode allows you to play without any expeditation.For those who want to enjoy a relaxing studio life without the expiration of their time, you can go through the game at your own pace.

        Interaction Events

        The charm of the characters.

        We have added an interaction event with the major characters from this series.A new aspect and charm of characters that were not painted on the original version.

        Professor Inglide Project

        This is a challenge that will help you mark the path of attack.

        You can quickly solve the question of what to do next" that is unique to a highly free RPG.

        The screen photo is in development of the PlayStation 5 version.

        How are ratings calculated?
        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
